<body> 
  <div class="content container-fluid" style="text-align:center;">
    <h2>Step 2. Select Your Payment Provider</h2>
     	<p>Upgrade to the Professional version of Friend Manager's Invite All Friends Extension </p>
	<p>For a one time fee of ${{app.price}} {{app.currency_code}}, once activated your extension will automatically scroll and<br>
	   select all of your friends in just one click. No more carpal tunnel, no more hours and hours spent clicking!<br></p>
	<h3>Don't delay, get your license today!</h3>
    <div id="paymentOptions">
	  {{#each paymentOptions}}
	  	{{#if isGoogleUser }}
	  		{{#isNotGoogleCheckout name}} 
	  			<a class='paymentOption'><img class='checkoutButton' src="{{buttonURL}}" onclick="initializeCheckout('{{name}}')"></a>
	  		{{/isNotGoogleCheckout}}
	  		{{else}}
	  			<a class='paymentOption'><img class='checkoutButton' src="{{buttonURL}}" onclick="initializeCheckout('{{name}}')"></a>
	  	{{/if}}
	  {{/each}}
    </div><br>
	<p>* If you are having trouble activating your license and keep geting prompted for payment, there is a possibility something<br>
	 on your computer is blocking activation. Please disable any security software or pop-up blockers.<br></p>
	<p>Still having trouble? Click <a href="http://kickasschromeapps.com/support/">here</a> for support.</p></p>
  </div>
  <script type='text/javascript'>
  	function initializeCheckout(name) {
  		window.location.replace('/initCheckout/' + name);
  	}
  </script>
